localized_changelogs.en:
We welcome the new version of OctoGram 2.0.0

We've essentially rebuilt OctoGram from the ground up, using the default Telegram code. 
What does this mean? Quicker updates, and quicker bugfixes!
There are plenty of cool new features, like the ability to hide stories, hide dividers dividers, play around with custom emojis, and a bunch more.

For now, we've put OTA updates on pause (they'll be back on the second release, promise), and third-party translations have been removed (they're not forgotten, though).

From this version on, the privacy policy is also available on the site. For more information, scroll to the bottom of the site.
